altername_name: PlayStation Demo Disc, Demo 1, Demo One (Version 2)
name: Demo One: Version 2 [SCES-00120]
overview: Demo disc for PlayStation that came bundled with the console. This is version 2 for Europe/UK/AUS. Playable demos: Battle Arena Toshinden Destruction Derby ESPN Extreme Games Jumping Flash Loaded Novastorm Total NBA '96 (controllable camera) Wipeout Trailers: Air Combat Assault Rigs Krazy Ivan Rapid Reload Ridge Racer Tekken Twisted Metal Starblade Alpha Warhawk Other: Dino Manta V-CD
